{"type": "article", "id": 42031, "title": "想光脚在户外玩耍？试试这双垫子｜这个设计了不起", "description": "我们每天都为你推荐几个最近发现的好设计。", "date": "2017-06-15T23:10:03Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 271, "name": "工业设计"}, {"id": 41488, "name": "Above The Fray"}, {"id": 41489, "name": "Case Studyo"}, {"id": 41490, "name": "Abeego"}, {"id": 41491, "name": "Caribou Creative"}, {"id": 41492, "name": "Piet Parra"}], "category": 17, "column": 38, "author": 400262, "comment_count": 11, "praise_count": 194, "image": "img/article/article_show/20170615222607KVXxHBRE9qGPtu3y.jpg", "contents": "<p nocleanhtml=\"true\">        <style type=\"text/css\"> p.p1 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; line-height: 27.0px; font: 18.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #323333} p.p2 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 18.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #323333; min-height: 25.0px} p.p3 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; line-height: 27.0px; font: 18.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #363636} p.p4 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; line-height: 27.0px; font: 18.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #363636; min-height: 25.0px} p.p5 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; line-height: 32.0px; font: 18.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #363636} p.p6 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; line-height: 32.0px; font: 18.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #363636; min-height: 25.0px} span.s1 {font-kerning: none} span.s2 {font-kerning: none; color: #363636} </style>  </p><p>我们每天都为你推荐几个最近发现的好设计。</p><p>「这个设计了不起」的微信公众号上线啦，直接搜索「BestDesign」或是「Qthings」就可以订阅，关注我们每日发现的新鲜好设计。</p><h3>Nakefit</h3><p>夏天外出游玩时，你有没有想摆脱人字拖的束缚赤脚行走的冲动？为了让人们能够安全、尽兴地玩耍，一支来自意大利的设计团队研发了一款名为 Nakefit 的脚垫，由弹性材质制成的它就像是一层保护膜，具备防水、防滑的特性，穿脱也相当方便。这是它的<a href=\"https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/1840198615/nakefit\" rel=\"nofollow\">众筹链接</a>，10 双一组的售价从 30 欧元起。<br></p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170615222718r9REFmThxDUfHeSV.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.553125\" data-format=\"gif\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170615222717mfCEGD1JW8RTrto0.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.574572\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170615222717JPAFg3NCD5jTnGYp.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.574572\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>LaMetric Time</h3><p>既然我们每天会收到各类手机应用的推送轰炸，为什么不让它们的呈现方式变得更有趣呢？英国设计团队 LaMetric 为此将推送与手机“分家”，打造了一款同名的智能闹钟，用户可以通过它的应用或是 IFTTT 设置推送逻辑，即便不拿起手机也能从一方小巧的像素风屏幕中了解所需要的讯息。这是它的<a href=\"https://www.amazon.com/LaMetric-Time-Wi-Fi-Clock-Smart/dp/B01IVTVK3W\" rel=\"nofollow\">购买链接</a>，售价为 199 美元。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170615222750fZDxdMk8L0iU2eNm.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667619\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170615222750vy8VcQAN5x32Iu01.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170615222750x7N49RGhJobWPzHc.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667619\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170615222751TX4tQxUWwJ0ab1rC.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.619048\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>PowerPlay by Above The Fray</h3><p>想要拥有一张整洁的办公桌，首要解决的问题或许就是那些总是纠缠不清的充电线了。这款来自美国日用配件品牌 <a href=\"https://abovethefray.co/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Above The Fray</a> 的 PowerPlay 收线器看起来就像是给适配器打造的一件皮革小马甲，充电时只要通过切口将电线抽出至需要的即可，不会让桌面看起来太过杂乱。这是它的<a href=\"https://abovethefray.co/products/powerplay-macbookpro-cable-organizer\" rel=\"nofollow\">购买链接</a>，售价为 35 美元。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170615222823wJZlbY2j5F3Rdv0Q.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666973\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170615222823xa6KpOQDuWAdb1XI.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666973\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170615222823ATCjg5Pxomqb6iu2.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666973\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>GIVE UP lamp by Piet Parra &amp; Case Studyo</h3><p>比利时艺术创意机构 <a href=\"http://www.casestudyo.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Case Studyo</a> 曾在 2015 年联手以超现实主义风格见长的荷兰艺术家 <a href=\"https://byparra.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Piet Parra</a> 打造了一个穿着高跟鞋的番茄雕塑作品 GIVE UP。最近，他们将这个有趣的拟人化形象改造成了一盏灯饰，即使是放在角落也能轻松地吸引到人们的注意。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201706152228364Tlvm7EXV2UCbYok.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.077895\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170615222835iuM4GQ1qaIzSvpRA.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666992\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Abeego by Caribou Creative</h3><p>成立于 2008 年的 <a href=\"https://canada.abeego.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Abeego</a> 是一个致力于用可重复使用的环保材料替代塑料保鲜袋的加拿大食品包装品牌，最近创意公司 <a href=\"https://www.cariboucreative.ca/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Caribou Creative</a> 为其重新设计了六款产品包装。在纸盒正面，除了基本信息的罗列之外，设计团队还根据包装袋的尺寸配上了食物插图，引导顾客购买所需要的款式。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170615222856lnUJ6M8P1fSiybhz.jpeg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201706152228567czKkxXQo382ADbL.jpeg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170615222856DCq7ZlyE9c8ivL3p.jpeg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170615222857wRdVtbEayBZNQmzo.jpeg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Floral Tea Story by Marina Malinovaya</h3><p>来自俄罗斯的 Marina Malinovaya 既是艺术家也是一名茶叶爱好者，在这套名为 Floral Tea Story 的摄影作品中，她将花叶与精致的茶具组合在一起，布置成仿佛可以闻到香气的花茶。俯拍的角度下，这些散落在桌面上的植物变成了倾泻而下的茶水或是散发出的热气，看起来相当优雅。如果你喜欢这种风格，还可以关注 Malinovava 的 <a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/marinamalinovaya/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Instagram</a>。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170615222948NwuagAtJ01Zly2eh.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"medium-insert-image-active\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"medium-insert-caption-placeholder\"></figcaption></figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170615222948WUkHia5dITBtYhuK.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170615222948WfqRESJvTnU7Vs2y.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170615222949ckKtOIJ4Wz1LBw6a.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>"}